Making flex look vertical in bootstrap - "flex-column"
For ease of access,the title and paragragh can be added immediately under the image in the post.html not using the col and row div tag.
&nbsp;  - This tag is used to give space in a paragraph's beginning or the beginning of a word,After a word and in a word it means (None breaking space.)
&cent;  - For cent sign
&yen;   - For yen sign
&pound; - For pound sign
&euro;  - For euro sign
&copy;  - For copyright sign
&reg;   - For registered trademark